<item>
            <title>[LU-7505] A released file lease cannot be taken again</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7505</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Taking a lease, releasing it and then taking it again will fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;llapi_lease_get(fd, LL_LEASE_RDLCK);   -&amp;gt; returns 0
llapi_lease_put(fd);                   -&amp;gt; returns LL_LEASE_RDLCK
llapi_lease_check(fd)                  -&amp;gt; returns 0 = no lease
llapi_lease_get(fd, LL_LEASE_RDLCK);   -&amp;gt; return -EBUSY
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/13441&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/13441&lt;/a&gt; has a commented out reproducer. Change the &quot;#if 0&quot; to &quot;#if 1&quot; in swap_layout_test.c:test15().&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
